{"id":160947,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/06/译者-《译者》每日原文推荐-2011613/","date":"2011-06-14T10:00:35Z","modified":"2011-06-14T17:36:15Z","title":"译者 | 《译者》每日原文推荐  2011/6/13","content":"<p><p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以下为每日原文推荐。如果你有兴趣，请参与翻译并将译文寄给</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://yyyyiiii.blogspot.com/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《译者》</span></a><b>(</b><span><b><span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"mailto:iyizhe@gmail.com\"><span>iyizhe@gmail.com</span></a>)</span></b></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">以便与大家共享。欢迎使用</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://feedburner.google.com/fb/a/mailverify?uri=yizhe&#038;loc=en_US\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">邮件组</span></a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">、</span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://goo.gl/f1NDK\">Google Reader</a><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和推特（</span><span><span>@yigroup</span></span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">）跟踪我们的最新消息。</span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【热点时评】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《环球邮报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.theglobeandmail.com/news/world/asia-pacific/chinese-dissident-hu-jia-to-be-released-but-ordeal-isnt-over/article2058046/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国异议人士胡佳出狱在即，但困境远未结束</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“中国现在的政治环境比他入狱时更加糟糕”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《巴尔的摩太阳报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.baltimoresun.com/business/sns-rt-us-rights-china-hactre75b14j-20110612,0,5394613.story\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">对于中国的维权人士来说，黑客攻击司空见惯</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">好莱坞记者</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/news/china-indie-director-persists-censorship-197093\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">尽管有审查、缺资金，中国独立电影导演仍然坚持拍片</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国内外</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.insideoutchina.com/2011/06/li-zhuang-returns-home-fang-hongs.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">李庄出狱回家了，方洪一家却消失了</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《印度时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://timesofindia.indiatimes.com/world/china/China-confess-a-kickback-websites-draw-inspiration-from-India/articleshow/8835472.cms\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的举报贿赂网站从印度获得灵感</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——但中国的领导人有印度领导人那么宽容吗？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《印度日报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.thehindu.com/news/international/article2096599.ece\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国内地的红色复兴</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——从延安到重庆“三十年来国家的重点在经济建设，但是我们的道德价值观全没了”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“如是说”分析</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.alsosprachanalyst.com/economy/british-empire-united-states-of-america-and-peoples-republic-of-china.html?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+AlsoSprachAnalyst+%28Also+sprach+Analyst+%28Main%29%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">大英帝国、美利坚合众国、还有中华人民共和国</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——大国崛起无征兆</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"OLE_LINK4\"></a><a rel=\"nofollow\" name=\"OLE_LINK3\"><span></span></a><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/11/world/asia/11mongolia.html?partner=rssnyt&#038;emc=rss\"><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">内蒙古的少数民族抗议，远非一日之寒</span></span></span><span><span></span></span></a></span><span><span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——“我们觉得快被汉人淹没了”</span></span></span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《卫报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2011/jun/13/china-riots-enter-third-day\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国骚乱进入第三天</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——因治安队与小贩之间的争执，引发了广州地区最严重骚乱</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-06-13/china-cracks-down-on-local-officials-in-wake-of-riots-bombs.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">骚乱与爆炸案频发，中国开始整治地方官员</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——治标不治本，能有多大效果？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交学者》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://the-diplomat.com/2011/06/12/how-china-can-avoid-next-conflict/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国如何避免下一场冲突</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中越这对老冤家同样固执，但他们也同样不想发生武装冲突。</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">国际经济法与政策博客</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://worldtradelaw.typepad.com/ielpblog/2011/06/is-chinese-investment-in-africa-neo-colonialism.html?utm_source=feedburner&#038;utm_medium=feed&#038;utm_campaign=Feed%3A+ielpblog+%28International+Economic+Law+and+Policy+Blog%29\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国对非洲投资是“新殖民主义”吗？</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——希拉里似乎作出了这样的暗示</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《时代》周刊</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.time.com/time/world/article/0,8599,2077139,00.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国的“财富外逃”</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——新迹象表明中国富人向国外移民</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美国梦醒博客</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://endoftheamericandream.com/archives/china-wants-to-construct-a-50-square-mile-self-sustaining-city-south-of-boise-idaho\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国即将在美国建设第一个经济特区</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国机械工业集团将在爱达荷州投资建设特区</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/06/10/us-markets-stocks-adrs-idUSTRE75969320110610\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">分析：投资者大量抛售中国上市公司股票，对大公司和</span>IPO<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">回避不迭</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">程致宇</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://chovanec.wordpress.com/2011/06/11/property-peak-growing-unrest-and-other-tidbits/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">房地产顶峰、动荡加剧和其它思考</span></a> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《纽约时报》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.nytimes.com/2011/06/14/world/asia/14china.html?_r=1&#038;partner=rss&#038;emc=rss\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国高速火车放慢脚步</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——星期一北京有</span><span>100</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">多名复员军人及其家属到铁道部门前抗议</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">欧亚评论</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.eurasiareview.com/china%E2%80%99s-fishing-ban-in-south-china-sea-implications-for-territorial-disputes-analysis-13062011/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国在南海发布禁渔令，对于领土争端有何影响</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.reuters.com/article/2011/06/12/us-southchinasea-idUSTRE75B0TY20110612\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">南中国海海上疆界争端的一些历史事实</span></a></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110612/ap_on_re_as/as_vietnam_china_protest\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">数百越南人举行反华游行</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中越在南海的争执引发新抗议</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">花岗斋杂记</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://granitestudio.org/2011/06/13/book-review-alan-paul-big-in-china/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">书评：《</span>Big in China<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">》</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——对于来到中国生活的外国人，首先要做的是别太把自己当回事</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span> </span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">【社会百态】</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">路透社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/nm/20110612/bs_nm/us_china_economy_inflation\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">专家称中国六月的通货膨胀率有可能达到</span>6%</a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——张卓元称全年</span><span>CPI</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">涨幅可能会到</span><span>5%</span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">美联社</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://news.yahoo.com/s/ap/20110612/ap_on_re_as/as_china_lead_poisoning\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国</span>600<span lang=\"ZH-CN\">多人铅中毒</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——其中有</span><span>103</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">位儿童</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span>MIT – <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://globalchange.mit.edu/files/document/MITJPSPGC_Rpt196.pdf\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">空气污染给中国带来的健康危害</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">（</span><span>25</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">页的深度报告）——</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">“</span><span>2005</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">年空气污染给中国经济多增加了</span><span>1120</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">亿美元的健康负担”</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《商业周刊》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.businessweek.com/news/2011-06-13/chinese-go-on-global-homebuying-spree-as-local-markets-tighten.html\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">中国人来到全球市场上狂购房产</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——世界各地房地产都会出现泡沫？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《福布斯》</span><span><span>  </span>&#8211;<span>  </span><a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://blogs.forbes.com/pauldenlinger/2011/06/10/apples-layered-strategy-translates-into-china-advantage/\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">苹果公司的层次化战略在中国占有优势</span></a></span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——比</span><span>Google</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">和</span><span>facebook</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">更灵活</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">《外交政策》</span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\"> </span><span>– <a rel=\"nofollow\" href=\"http://www.foreignpolicy.com/articles/2011/06/10/the_big_test\"><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">大考</span></a> </span><span lang=\"ZH-CN\">——中国的高考是否能筛选出最优秀的人才呢？</span><span></span></p>\n<p><span 